# Publish workflow

After editing workshop tracks or catalog content:

1. Run `make publish` (commits, pushes to GitHub, pushes all tracks to Instruqt).
2. Or manually: `git add -A && git commit && git push` then `make push-all`.

Never leave track changes only on disk — always push to both remotes.
